#h2: Bold Formatting

#p: This has #**"bold" text in it.

#p: This has #b"also bold" text too.

#p: Bracketed bold: [#b : bold text] in a sentence.

#p: Bracketed star form: [#** : also works] like this.

#h2: Italic Formatting

#p: This has #__"italic" text in it.

#p: This has #i"also italic" text too.

#p: Bracketed italic: [#i : italic text] in a sentence.

#h2: Links

#p: Visit [#url link="https://example.com" text="Example Site"] today.

#h2: Nesting

#p: Here is [#i : [#b : bold inside italic]] text.

#p: Here is [#b : [#i : italic inside bold]] text.

#h2: Mixed Inline

#p: A line with #**"bold" and #__"italic" and [#url link="https://example.com" text="a link"] together.
